  <h2>6. Managing Cookies</h2>
  <h3>6.1 Browser Settings</h3>
  <p>
    Most web browsers allow you to control cookies through their settings preferences. You can set your browser to refuse cookies or delete certain cookies. However, if you disable cookies, some features of our website may not function properly. Here are links to help you manage cookies in popular browsers:
