  <h2>7. Web Beacons and Similar Technologies</h2>
  <p>
    In addition to cookies, we use other technologies to enhance your experience:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Local Storage:</strong> Stores your theme preferences and session data locally in your browser. This data never leaves your device.</li>
    <li><strong>Session Storage:</strong> Temporary data stored for a single browsing session (e.g., scroll position during page transitions).</li>
    <li><strong>Web Beacons (Pixel Tags):</strong> Small images in emails that track opens and clicks (only with your consent for marketing emails).</li>
    <li><strong>Service Workers:</strong> Background scripts that enable offline functionality and faster page loads.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    These technologies respect your consent preferences and are subject to the same privacy protections outlined in our Privacy Policy.
  </p>

  <h2>8. Updates to This Cookie Policy</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices, technology, or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the updated policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date. We encourage you to review this Cookie Policy periodically to stay informed about how we use cookies.
  </p>

